##edge-user: scope is for services running on edge device, manipulating data
user edge-user
topic readwrite edge/#
topic readwrite external/#
topic readwrite customer/#
topic read machine/#
topic read UNS/#
topic read $SYS/#
#v1 alarmservice temp exposure (legacy)
topic readwrite Alarms/#
topic readwrite ConnectedClients/#

##machine-user: is for machine controllers to have a space to store data into the broker
user machine-user
topic readwrite machine/#
topic readwrite Marel/#
topic read edge/#
topic read UNS/#
pattern readwrite edge/%c/#
#v1 alarmservice temp exposure (legacy)
topic readwrite Alarms/#
topic readwrite ConnectedClients/#

##uns-user: gateway from and to edge<>UNS
user uns-user
topic readwrite UNS/#
topic readwrite edge/#
topic read dcm/#
##customer facing data
user customer-user
topic readwrite customer/#

##external facing data, e.g. 3rd party
user external-user
topic readwrite external/#

##root user
user swsdev
topic readwrite #
topic read $SYS/#

##hmi-user: interaction from broker to HMI mqtt-service
user hmi-user
topic read edge/+/#
topic readwrite edge/hmi/#
topic readwrite edge/+/desired/#
topic readwrite edge/+/+/desired/#
topic readwrite edge/+/+/+/desired/#
topic readwrite edge/+/commands/#
topic readwrite edge/+/+/commands/#
topic readwrite edge/+/+/+/commands/#

## bridges UNS between different brokers
user bridge
topic readwrite UNS/#

# This affects access control for clients with no username

# This affects all clients.
pattern readwrite system/client/%c/#
